Description: Implements the method introduced in Wiegand, V., Hennessey, A., Tench, C. R., & Mahlberg, M. (2017), "Comparing co-occurrences between corpora". 38th ICAME conference, Charles University, Prague. It identifies significant difference in co-occurrence counts for a given node or set of nodes across two corpora, using a Fisherâ€™s Exact test.
